<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blacklisted</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: white;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 45px;
            line-height: 0.5;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }

        .content p {
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .content .details {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content" >
        <h2>Warning</h2>
        <p>You are blacklisted.</p>
        <div class="details" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;flex-direction: column;">
            <p>This action has been taken due to unauthorized activities detected on your account. Such activities include, but are not limited to:</p>
            <ul style="display: flex;flex-direction: column;width: fit-content;text-align: left;">
                <li>Violation of terms of service</li>
                <li>Suspicious login attempts</li>
                <li>Malicious behavior</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
